<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 02:15:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着捐款枯竭，以色列司法政变背后的智囊团正在缩减其业务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/as-donations-dry-up-think-tank-behind-israels-judicial-coup-scales-back-operations/0000018e-a141-d176-adcf-a14d08d50000</link><description>据报道，科赫莱特政策论坛是政府试图进行司法改革的关键参与者，该论坛正在削减业务，解雇了数十名研究人员，并削减了对其他支持类似目标的右翼组织的支持</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 00:17:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/as-donations-dry-up-think-tank-behind-israels-judicial-coup-scales-back-operations/0000018e-a141-d176-adcf-a14d08d50000</guid></item><item><title>被杀的埃塞俄比亚裔以色列青少年的家人谴责枪杀他的警察无罪释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-slain-ethiopian-israeli-teen-decry-acquittal-of-police-officer-who-shot-him/0000018e-a078-ded0-a18f-e2f88fef0000</link><description>所罗门·特卡 (Solomon Teka) 在 2019 年公园的一起事件中被杀。他的妹妹在谈到判决时表示，“警方现在有权杀害儿童”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 23:08:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-03/ty-article/.premium/family-of-slain-ethiopian-israeli-teen-decry-acquittal-of-police-officer-who-shot-him/0000018e-a078-ded0-a18f-e2f88fef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方消息人士：加沙援助人员被杀是因为“以色列国防军军官在当地为所欲为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-sources-gaza-aid-workers-killed-because-officers-on-the-ground-do-what-they-want/0000018e-a06e-d9c2-afbe-a8fe319b0000</link><description>以色列国防军和国防部声称援助人员被杀是由于协调不力造成的。以色列军方消息人士后来驳斥了他们的说法，称该事件“与协调无关”，而是“每个指挥官都为自己制定规则”造成的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 20:49:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-sources-gaza-aid-workers-killed-because-officers-on-the-ground-do-what-they-want/0000018e-a06e-d9c2-afbe-a8fe319b0000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列将所有加沙受害者视为公关灾难就好了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-02/ty-article/.highlight/if-only-israel-thought-of-all-its-gaza-victims-as-a-pr-disaster/0000018e-9fe4-d4c8-adce-fff46a8a0000</link><description>以色列对七名世界中央厨房援助人员在以色列袭击中丧生的反应与其对之前整个加沙冲突期间发生的人道主义悲剧的反应形成鲜明对比</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 19:44:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-04-02/ty-article/.highlight/if-only-israel-thought-of-all-its-gaza-victims-as-a-pr-disaster/0000018e-9fe4-d4c8-adce-fff46a8a0000</guid></item><item><title>数百名以色列人在内塔尼亚胡位于耶路撒冷的家外抗议，警察与人质家庭发生冲突；五人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/police-hostage-families-clash-as-hundreds-rally-outside-pm-home-in-jerusalem-5-arrested/0000018e-9feb-d4f2-a9cf-bfff4a830000</link><description>数百名抗议者中断了数千名以色列人参加的示威活动，呼吁提前举行选举并立即达成人质协议，这是为期四天的大规模反政府集会的一部分</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 18:52:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/police-hostage-families-clash-as-hundreds-rally-outside-pm-home-in-jerusalem-5-arrested/0000018e-9feb-d4f2-a9cf-bfff4a830000</guid></item><item><title>惠誉确认以色列信用评级，但给予其负面展望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/fitch-affirms-israels-credit-rating-but-assigns-it-a-negative-outlook/0000018e-9fb8-d4f2-a9cf-bfbe09860000</link><description>国际评级机构批评内塔尼亚胡政府，称联盟的不稳定阻碍了财政整顿。 “尽管赤字激增，2024 年预算修正案仍包括一些与联盟相关的支出”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 17:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/fitch-affirms-israels-credit-rating-but-assigns-it-a-negative-outlook/0000018e-9fb8-d4f2-a9cf-bfbe09860000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗对真主党和叙利亚的关键人物：据称在大马士革被以色列暗杀的最高将军是谁？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-point-man-to-hezbollah-who-is-the-top-general-allegedly-assassinated-by-israel/0000018e-9f9c-d9c2-afbe-bfde685a0000</link><description>扎赫迪20岁时加入革命卫队，担任空军指挥官、地面部队指挥官和作战部门负责人。在他最后的职位上，他是圣城军叙利亚和黎巴嫩指挥官，被认为与纳斯鲁拉关系特别密切</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 17:45:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-point-man-to-hezbollah-who-is-the-top-general-allegedly-assassinated-by-israel/0000018e-9f9c-d9c2-afbe-bfde685a0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登“将向以色列明确表示”必须保护加沙援助人员；美国期待“全面”公开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-demands-swift-probe-u-k-summons-israeli-envoy-world-reacts-to-wck-attack/0000018e-9f72-ded0-a18f-dff2c6500000</link><description>该非政府组织表示，周一，世界中央厨房的七名工作人员在以色列对加沙中部的空袭中丧生，其中包括来自澳大利亚、英国和波兰的公民。英国已召见以色列大使，阿联酋宣布将停止海上援助路线的努力</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:35:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/u-s-demands-swift-probe-u-k-summons-israeli-envoy-world-reacts-to-wck-attack/0000018e-9f72-ded0-a18f-dff2c6500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战第 179 天：将向哈马斯提交新的停火提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-179-new-cease-fire-proposal-to-be-presented-to-hamas/0000018e-9f6f-d4f2-a9cf-bf7f33f30000</link><description>以色列空袭导致加沙七名国际援助人员死亡 ■ 以色列国防军调查发现，保护车队的部队误认为武装恐怖分子与他们同行 ■ 以色列发动的空袭导致伊朗在叙利亚的高级将军丧生，伊朗最高领导人表示，以色列“将对这次袭击感到遗憾” ■ 摩萨德称将向哈马斯提交新的停火/释放人质提案 ■ 战争结束 179 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:26:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-179-new-cease-fire-proposal-to-be-presented-to-hamas/0000018e-9f6f-d4f2-a9cf-bf7f33f30000</guid></item><item><title>“极端正统派正处于权力巅峰，但不要参军。这让以色列人发疯”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-04-02/ty-article-podcast/ultra-orthodox-israelis-are-at-the-peak-of-their-power-but-dont-pay-the-price-of-war/0000018e-9e50-dc54-a19f-9e7cac2f0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:13:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-04-02/ty-article-podcast/ultra-orthodox-israelis-are-at-the-peak-of-their-power-but-dont-pay-the-price-of-war/0000018e-9e50-dc54-a19f-9e7cac2f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列侨民部长谴责美国“更难”释放加沙人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-blasts-u-s-for-making-gaza-hostage-release-harder/0000018e-9f4d-d6b5-a39f-bf5dc27d0000</link><description>阿米猜·奇克利部长公开抨击美国对拉法的立场，并指责抗议运动是“邪恶的”，并鼓励恐怖分子</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 16:11:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-minister-blasts-u-s-for-making-gaza-hostage-release-harder/0000018e-9f4d-d6b5-a39f-bf5dc27d0000</guid></item><item><title>10万人签署请愿书，要求撤销10月7日以色列人质进入加沙照片的奖项</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/100-000-sign-petition-to-revoke-award-for-oct-7-photo-of-israeli-taken-hostage-into-gaza/0000018e-9f11-d9c2-afbe-bfd713000000</link><description>这张由美联社摄影师拍摄的照片显示，哈马斯武装分子将一名以色列人的尸体抬进加沙地带。请愿书呼吁撤回，以“发出尊重新闻业人类尊严和道德标准的强烈信息”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 15:48:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/100-000-sign-petition-to-revoke-award-for-oct-7-photo-of-israeli-taken-hostage-into-gaza/0000018e-9f11-d9c2-afbe-bfd713000000</guid></item><item><title>“臭氧恐慌”之后，备受争议的减肥药 Wegovy 获准在以色列使用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/after-ozempic-panic-controversial-weight-loss-drug-wegovy-approved-for-use-in-israel/0000018e-9b15-dd2b-ad9f-db5fe8e60000</link><description>在 FDA 批准三年后，Wegovy 现在可以在以色列通过处方购买，起价为每月 600 谢克尔（163 美元）。一些医生预计非肥胖患者的需求量很大，就像在美国一样：“以色列人在这些事情上倾向于模仿美国”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 14:56:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/after-ozempic-panic-controversial-weight-loss-drug-wegovy-approved-for-use-in-israel/0000018e-9b15-dd2b-ad9f-db5fe8e60000</guid></item><item><title>赤脚奔跑：流离失所的加沙人在战区赤脚行走</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-run-barefoot-displaced-gazans-are-going-without-shoes-in-a-war-zone/0000018e-99af-de2c-afff-bbefb0970000</link><description>在逃离空袭或按照以色列国防军的命令向南撤离时，许多加沙人没有合适的鞋子离开家。现在，几个月后，许多人在瓦砾、玻璃和其他碎片上行走了数英里以躲避轰炸</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 14:23:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-04-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-run-barefoot-displaced-gazans-are-going-without-shoes-in-a-war-zone/0000018e-99af-de2c-afff-bbefb0970000</guid></item><item><title>西班牙总理表示将于七月前承认巴勒斯坦国家地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/spain-to-recognize-palestinian-statehood-by-july-prime-minister-says/0000018e-9f0d-d6b5-a39f-bf5d22770000</link><description>桑切斯表示，他相信欧盟内部很快就会出现“临界群体”，推动多个成员国采取同样的立场</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 14:08:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/spain-to-recognize-palestinian-statehood-by-july-prime-minister-says/0000018e-9f0d-d6b5-a39f-bf5d22770000</guid></item><item><title>以色列从“影子战争”转向对伊朗的直接和明确的打击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/assassinations-leave-u-s-with-dilemma-on-how-to-de-escalate-israel-iran-shadow-war/0000018e-9ebe-d9c2-afbe-befe4fbd0000</link><description>伊朗对圣城军高级将军穆罕默德·礼萨·扎赫迪周一在大马士革遇刺事件的反应有四种可能的情况</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 13:49:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/assassinations-leave-u-s-with-dilemma-on-how-to-de-escalate-israel-iran-shadow-war/0000018e-9ebe-d9c2-afbe-befe4fbd0000</guid></item><item><title>所有这些纽约犹太人都希望释放以色列人质。那么他们为什么要分别举行抗议活动呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/all-these-n-y-jews-want-israeli-hostages-released-so-why-are-they-at-separate-protests/0000018e-9e53-dc54-a19f-9e7f15830000</link><description>周日，纽约人可以在三个不同的集会中进行选择，要求释放加沙哈马斯扣押的人质。这就是三个抗议团体意见不一致的地方</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 13:47:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/all-these-n-y-jews-want-israeli-hostages-released-so-why-are-they-at-separate-protests/0000018e-9e53-dc54-a19f-9e7f15830000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军无人机对世界中央厨房援助车队进行了三次轰炸，目标是不在场的武装哈马斯成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-bombed-wck-aid-convoy-3-times-targeting-armed-hamas-member-who-wasnt-there/0000018e-9e75-d764-adff-9eff29360000</link><description>援助车队沿以色列军队批准的路线行驶，袭击造成世界中央厨房的七名工人死亡，但目标是一名被认为是恐怖分子的武装人员，他从未与车辆一起离开仓库</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 12:03:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-bombed-wck-aid-convoy-3-times-targeting-armed-hamas-member-who-wasnt-there/0000018e-9e75-d764-adff-9eff29360000</guid></item><item><title>获释人质玛雅·雷格夫：加沙的每位女性人质都遭受过性虐待</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostage-maya-regev-every-woman-hostage-in-gaza-experiences-sexual-abuse/0000018e-9e09-d764-adff-9ecfce650000</link><description>雷格夫与其他获释人质和人质亲属在议会委员会上发表了讲话。获释人质莎朗·库尼奥-阿洛尼（Sharon Cunio-Alony）的丈夫仍被哈马斯关押在加沙，她敦促立法者不要忘记这些人：“他们也受到虐待”</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 10:56:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostage-maya-regev-every-woman-hostage-in-gaza-experiences-sexual-abuse/0000018e-9e09-d764-adff-9ecfce650000</guid></item><item><title>法院将对被指控在 2019 年杀害埃塞俄比亚以色列人的警察做出裁决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/court-to-rule-on-police-officer-accused-of-killing-ethiopian-israeli-in-2019/0000018e-9d52-dc54-a19f-9f7e39420000</link><description>这名被指控犯有过失杀人罪的警官向地面开枪，一枚跳弹击中了 18 岁的所罗门·特卡 (Solomon Teka)，导致他死亡。由于事件发生后他的生命受到威胁，宣读判决期间预计会有严密的安保措施</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Apr 2024 08:55:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-02/ty-article/.premium/court-to-rule-on-police-officer-accused-of-killing-ethiopian-israeli-in-2019/0000018e-9d52-dc54-a19f-9f7e39420000</guid></item></channel></rss>